{
"#name"
:
{
"x weixin"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"微信群机器人"
,
"en"
:
"WeChat iLink bot"
}
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"使用 x weixin 向你的微信群发送消息。首次使用需要通过 QR 码登录配置。"
,
"en"
:
"Use x weixin to send messages to your WeChat group. First use requires QR code login configuration."
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"en"
:
"- Interactive env use `x weixin login` to login via QR code. The credentials will be saved locally.\n- Run `x weixin --cfg token=<bot_token>` to set bot token directly.\n"
,
"cn"
:
"- 交互环境中可使用 `x weixin login` 进行 QR 码登录，凭证将保存到本地\n- 亦可运行命令 `x weixin --cfg token=<bot_token>` 直接设置机器人 token\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x weixin send --text \"Hello from WeChat bot\""
,
"cn"
:
"发送文本消息到微信群"
,
"en"
:
"Send text message to WeChat group"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x weixin send --image /path/to/image.jpg"
,
"cn"
:
"发送图片到微信群"
,
"en"
:
"Send image to WeChat group"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x weixin send --file /path/to/file.pdf"
,
"cn"
:
"发送文件到微信群"
,
"en"
:
"Send file to WeChat group"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x weixin login"
,
"cn"
:
"QR 码登录微信机器人"
,
"en"
:
"Login to WeChat bot via QR code"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x weixin listen poll"
,
"cn"
:
"启动消息监听"
,
"en"
:
"Start listening for messages"
}
]
,
"#subcmd:常用"
:
[
"send"
,
"login"
]
,
"#subcmd:高级"
:
[
"listen"
]
,
"#subcmd:内部"
:
[
"--cfg"
,
"--cur"
]
,
